name: Bientot sur ce site: Nouveaux Artprints! / Coming soon: New Artprints!
'Cerf'/'Stag'
description:
The largest print to be released thus far from the HINEink studio. Big, bold and beautiful, the local stag gives rest to a collection of ‘Choucas’, a traditional alpine bird which is believed to offer reincarnation to climbers lost in the mountains. 

Edition of 150.
Signed and numbered by the artist.
Dimensions: 50cmx90cm. 
Giclee Print on 350gm 100% cotton Somerset fine art paper.

Price €120.

Shipped in 2mm wall 4" diameter extra strong postal tube.

name: 'L'Ours Et Les Oiseaux'/'The Bear And The Birds'
description:
The Brown Bear that once roamed freely in the high mountains of the Alps, is depicted here in black and white and brought to life with an explosion of wings and colour. Derived from an original mixed-media painting this Giclee print offers a variation on the more graphic artworks available through HINEink. 

Edition of 150.
Signed and numbered by the artist.
Dimensions: 60cmx60cm.
Giclee Print on 320gm Ultra-Smooth Italian fine art paper.

Price €100.

Shipped in 2mm wall 4" diameter extra strong postal tube.

name: 'Le Bouquetin'/'The Ibex' Original (Negative)
description:
The original contemporary Chamonix print. Derived from a hand inked illustration, this unique design features the valleys signature animal, le Bouquetin. Hidden within its shape are the significant titles of the valley; ‘Chamonix’ wrapping round its lower section, ‘Mont Blanc’ dropping vertically between its eyes, the names of  surrounding peaks forming the horns. A striking black and white composition that is available in two versions and on two paper options – Original or Deluxe.
 
2 versions available:

Original (Deluxe)-

Edition of 250.
Signed and numbered by the artist.
Dimensions: 42cmx59.4cm (A2).
Giclee Print on 350gsm 100% cotton Somerset fine art paper.

Price €80.

Original-

Open ended edition.
Signed by the artist.
Dimensions: 42cmx59.4cm (A2).
Giclee Print on 220gsm Ultra-Smooth Italian fine art paper.

Price €25.

Original deluxe shipped in 2mm wall 4" diameter extra strong postal tube.
Original shipped in 1.5mm wall 2" diameter postal tube.
